        <ontology:hasDescription>1) Threat on Sapmi terrritory driven by extrative industries (mining, logging, energy); 2) To maintain the knowledge and interest of Sami people in handcrafting. Overall the type of challenge faced by this VC is unspecified. This VC is classified as Traditional and Innovative.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


